OL,5,Cover pay
OL,7,FHospital porters, cleaners and
OL,8,Fcatering staff have launched a 48-hour
OL,9,Fstrike in a dispute over pay.
OL,11,FMembers of the GMB at and Broadgreen
OL,12,FHospital in Liverpool walked out after
OL,13,Fthe union said they missed out on a
OL,14,Flump sum payment because they were not
OL,15,Femployed directly by the NHS.
OL,17,FThe union warned of further strikes if
OL,18,Fthe dispute is not resolved.
