OL,5,Cover pay
OL,7,FKerry Nash, GMB senior organiser,
OL,8,Fsaid: "NHS workers put themselves on
OL,9,Fthe frontline during Covid and yet
OL,10,Fthey're missing out on this payment.
OL,12,F"They do the same work as many who
OL,13,Fhave received the payment, the only
OL,14,Fdifference is a name on their uniform
OL,15,For payslip.
OL,17,F"Their work is vital to the safe
OL,18,Frunning of our hospitals. The least
OL,19,Fthey deserve is fair treatment."
