OL,7,FA spokesman for Liverpool University
OL,8,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust said:
OL,9,F"This industrial action concerns a
OL,10,Fdispute between GMB members and their
OL,11,Fprevious employer.
OL,13,F"The Trust has followed national
OL,14,Fguidelines for non-consolidated pay
OL,15,Fawards.
OL,17,F"Our estates and facilities team has
OL,18,Fbusiness continuity plans in place to
OL,19,Fensure the safe delivery of care and
OL,20,Fpeople should attend their hospital
OL,21,Fappointments as planned."
